<br>
1.  never ever ever allow anyone under 60 into the group.  direct them to sebilis/velks.<br>
<br>
2.  warrior + 2 melee dps classes are all the dps needed for this.  more helps, obviously.<br>
<br>
3.  max haste and max buffs are a huge help. (i.e. paladin shaman enchanter ranger cleric.. ALL of them).<br>
<br>
4.  dont ever ever delay.. if a second goes by without you hitting something, trial is over.  we re made our assist keys to say /assist MT, /attack on.... no delays.  the MA needs to target QUICKLY.<br>
<br>
